  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nKeyword Rank Tracker\n\nTrack daily site rankings on Google, Bing, and YouTube. Monitor the top 100 search results on both desktop and mobile, and check your AI search visibility in ChatGPT, Perplexity, AIOs, and more.\n\nStart free trial\nRequest a demo\n\nNo credit card required\n\nDesktop\nMobile\nAI Overviews results\nYour keyword *\nYour domain (optional)\nCountry\nUSA\nLocation\nEnter city name\nLanguage\nEnglish\nCheck ranking\n\nYou have 5 free attempts left for today\n\nAll your ranking data. One powerful Keyword Checker. Zero hassle.\nRankings data\nSERP competitors\nHistorical data\nAI search visibility\nTrack your website’s keyword performance with detailed insights\n\nMonitor daily rankings on Google, Bing, Yahoo, and YouTube\n\nTrack the top 100 search results for any keyword\n\nCheck AI search visibility across ChatGPT, AI Overviews, AI Mode, Gemini, and Perplexity\n\nView desktop and mobile rankings\n\nAccess ranking data via API for seamless integration\n\nStart free trial\nBoost your agency’s SEO with the Keyword Position Checker\nAPI\n\nSeamlessly integrate the SEO Rank Tracker into your dashboards and tools. Pull real-time data on all tracked keywords, search engines, and locations to automate reporting, run bulk SEO analyses, and optimize workflows.\n\nWhite Label\n\nOffer clients a fully branded experience. Customize dashboards, logos, and URLs while showcasing your agency’s expertise by running SE Ranking’s SEO keyword rank tracking technology behind the scenes.\n\nReports\n\nGenerate unlimited automated reports, delivered straight to your clients’ inboxes from the Keyword Position Checker tool. Highlight daily, weekly, or monthly ranking changes, visibility trends, and SERP features using clear, engaging graphs and tables.\n\nStart free trial\nHow to use our Keyword Rank Tracker\nSee your rankings breakdown\n\nView your website’s daily rankings v",
